import View from "./view.js"; import icons from "../../img/icons.svg"; class RecipeView extends View { _parentElement = document.querySelector(".recipe"); _errorMessage = "we could not find recipe try the other one "; _message = ""; addHandlerRender(handler) { ["hashchange", "load"].forEach((ev) => window.addEventListener(ev, handler) ); } _generateMarkup() { return `
${ this._data.cookingTime } minutes
${ this._data.serving } servings

Recipe ingredients

    ${this._data.ingredients .map(this._generateMarkupIngrdeients) .join("")}

How to cook it

This recipe was carefully designed and tested by ${ this._data.publisher }. Please check out directions at their website.

Directions
`; } _generateMarkupIngrdeients(ing) { return `
  • ${ing.quantity}
    ${ing.unit} ${ing.description}
    • `; } } export default new RecipeView();
